These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, badminton, skateboarding, rowing
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Sport   | handball | badminton | skateboarding | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, sunflower, iris, lily
1. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Flower   | sunflower | orchid | lily | iris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
City: marseilles, san-francisco, colone, nizza
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| City   | marseilles | colone | san-francisco | nizza |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, havana, vegafina, game
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Cigar   | havana | dunhill | game | vegafina |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indian, pakistani, turkish
1. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
2. the indian is on the right of the pakistani##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Nationality   | turkish | pakistani | indian | dutch |

