2. the pilot is on the left or right of the videographer##3
3. the videographer is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the videographer is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| Job   | dressmaker | pilot | videographer | software-developer |

