2. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Pet   | rat | cat | snake | fish |

