2. the vegafina-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##2
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | alhambra | vegafina | old-henry | oliveros |

