1. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
3. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | funk | disco | jazz | indie |

