3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Flower   | daffodil | begonia | zinnia | balloon-flower |

 